  "description": "The anglerfish strategy. At pianissimo: total darkness, a sub-bass rumble barely present. At fortissimo: the lure fires — velCutoffAmt=1.0 opens the filter completely, a flash of brightness, a creature revealed. The prey does not understand what it sees until it is too late.",
