    "scripture": [
      "D001: velocity controls the cutoff. This is doctrine.",
      "At pianissimo: darkness. At fortissimo: the lure fires.",
      "The prey sees the light for 0.001 seconds before it understands the danger."
    ],
    "revelation": null,
    "god": null,
    "flock_note": "This preset REQUIRES velocity expression to reveal its nature. A static MIDI velocity reveals nothing — only the sub rumble. Sweep velocity from 1 to 127 on each note. The darkness gives way to the lure. CREATURE macro adds bioluminescent shimmer to the lure flash.",
    "diagnosis": "velCutoffAmt=1.0 — maximum D001 expression. At low velocity, filterCutoff=100 stays dark. At high velocity, cutoff sweeps up toward 800 Hz — the lure fires. bioMix=0.4 adds organic shimmer to the velocity response. bodyChar=0 (Open Water) keeps the lure clean, not industrial."
  },
